  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Two stage study looking at different titration schedules in patients with moderate to severe
      non-malignant chronic pain. Up to 80 patients at approximately 15 centers in the US to be
      enrolled. Study participation is approximately 3 months.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
